        <item>
            <title>Version 0.9.15</title>
            <pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 19:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>0.9.15</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.9.15</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.2</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>Menu bar popover UI refresh</h3>
                <ul>
                <li>New SwiftUI popover replaces the old NSMenu — live recording cell with breathing waveform, REC pill, mono timer</li>
                <li>Status-bar icon animates as a 5-bar waveform during recording</li>
                <li>Recent meeting rows: left-click opens transcript, right-click for context menu, red badge opens Tag Speakers</li>
                <li>Dark mode supported. Activity log moved to Settings.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Carries forward v0.9.14's voice re-check and SystemAudioBridge race fix.</p>
            ]]></description>
